/*


Ŀ
Funo     R911BrancoAutor     Marcos Simidu       Data  18.10.97 
Ĵ
Descrio  Layout da Listagem                                         
ٱ


*/
Static Function R911Branco()

While nLin<nLimPag
	FmtLin(Array(03),aL[13],,,@nLin)
EndDo
FmtLin(,aL[01],,,@nLin)

Return



